Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : snat n tilawin-agi țusemmant d waṭas n tilawin n Sinay i d-ițeddun si cceṛq alamma d lɣeṛb.
Taqbuct n leḥyuḍ n temdint-agi ɛedlen. Deg ussan-nni yufa-ten-id deg waṭas n uqehheṛ ; yusa-d si tmurt n Yahuda meṛṛa qebbeggren-d s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, s wurrif-nsen.
swan meṛṛa si lɛinseṛ n Sidi Ṛebbi i d-iteffɣen seg wezṛu iteddun yid-es azal n tnin n ddheb akk-d ddheb n lfeṭṭa akk-d wid iḍaɛen n leslak, qṛib a ten-t-id-issers ɣef tmura n ddunit meṛṛa ;
Taqbuct n leḥyuḍ n temdint-nni ɛedlen. Tețțɣeccirat, ffɣent-ed si leǧwahi n temdint, leḍyuṛ akk-d ț-țamdint.
Sin inigan-agi sɛan tazmert ad ilint ț-țamdint n Ṛejyu, țțawin-d imuḍan ɣer imukan n  akken i ten-id-ițeffɣen seg waṭas n yemdanen.
Yekna daɣen acḥal yelha m'ara n-aseɣ ɣuṛ-es, ad ikkat waḍu ɣer mkul ṣṣenf.
Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen yewwi-t-id ɣer leǧwahi n temdint n lǧil-agi yesɛan azal akteṛ n tmura n Ccekkaṛin n Benyamin, d nutni ẓran akk-d imeqqranen n tmurt n Jlili.
Tawaɣit tis snat tɛedda, ataya tețțeddu-d twaɣit tis snat.
Tafat n temdint n Tiṣalunik yumnen s Lmasiḥ ilaq ad heggin iman-is ɣer yemdanen n ddunit-agi i gețțumetlen yis-sen, ț-țamdint n Ṛuder.
Mmektit-ed belli ula d kečč ay imdanen ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail iṭṭef amkan deg webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi, yeččuṛen d leqwanen yeɛnan ddunit-agi.
Seg imiren aṭas n tilawin i gellan dinna, aṭas n lɣaci i gellan dinna, aṭas n wat Isṛail i gellan dinna, nutni daɣen i d-yețțasen s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi i d-ikkan s ɣuṛ-es.
Mmektit-ed kan iwakken aț-țesseɣlim seg wul, am akken i tsedqem wiyaḍ ; ur xeddmet ara ccehwat n tnefsit-nwen, ur txeddmem ara ayen i d-iɛeǧben i Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ur țțaket ara ayen yeṣfan i yeqjan, ur ṭeggiṛet ara tiɛeqcin ɣlayen zdat yilfan, m'ulac a ten ṛekḍen yerna a d-zzin fell-asen.
Yusa-d iwakken ad theddnen wulawen-iw yeṣfan, yewwi-yi-d yid-i ula d leǧnas nniḍen, ad slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, yerna a ten-id-yili d sebba n kra n wayen yellan deg-sen.
Lameɛna walan belli Sidi Ṛebbi iwekkel-it i wid ixeddmen lxiṛ, axaṭer ț-țideț. D ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa n Musa i ț-țamecṭuḥt.
Lameɛna abecceṛ n lexbaṛ n lxiṛ i tmura nniḍen akk-d țɛeggiyen yellan deg ubecceṛ n lexbaṛ n lxiṛ.
Ccix-nni n lewḥuc : wid iteddun ɣef wučči n tmurt n Maṣer armi ț-țamurt n Ilamen, meɛna llan wid ițwaḥesben iman-nsen d agdud n Sidna Musa akk-d wid ur nesɛi lfayda i d-iteddun iqettalen.
Llant aṭas n tutlayin yemxalafen di liman, sɛant akk lmeɛna.
Mačči d ayagi kan : arraw n Rbiḥa daɣen i gella yerna d azedganen m'ara slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, ilaq ad yili d ayen yelhan ama deg ul-is. Atah wayen yellan deg-nneɣ akteṛ n wiyaḍ, mačči d win yessimɣuṛen iman-is.
Lexbeṛ-agi n lxiṛ i tețwasellkem ma yella tettebɛem-t neɣ m'ulac imdanen, d ayen yesɛan azal akteṛ n wiyaḍ.
Iɣezṛan, idurar ț-țɣaltin ad uɣalen d izuɣaṛ ! Iberdan iɛewjen ad țțuseggmen, wid ixesṛen ad qeɛden .
Llan deg wazal n ṛebɛa alaf n yemdanen. Llan daɣen aṭas n yemdanen iqucaṛen akk-d wid i d-ițeffɣen seg waṭas n yemdanen.
Di leǧwahi-nni, tella yiwet n tqeḍɛit tameqqrant n yilfan i gkessen dinna.
Amdan yezmer ad iḥeṛṛeb yal ṣṣenf n lewḥuc : ama d wid iteddun ɣef ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen, ama d ifṛax, ama d izerman ama d lewḥuc n lebḥeṛ yerna ț-țideț iɣleb-iten meṛṛa.
Ilaq acḥal ayagi segmi i d-yețțaken tilawin yeṭṭfen deg umenɣi ɣef ddemma n lecɣal-nsen ; xḍu-k i tqeḍɛit ɣef yidaṛṛen-nsen iwakken ula d nutni.
Ma yella tețḍeggiɛem leṛẓaq n ddunit-agi, yeččuṛen ț-țamdint neɣ s wakka ara țcirin awal n Ṛebbi ; akka ara ama d-tban tmanegt n Baba-tneɣ Ṛebbi s wakka i ț-țismi ara ț-țismi ara d-yuɣal.
Ațan kra n yergazen n lǧiha-nni i gellan di temdint n Lquds yellan deg wusu-ines.
A nnger-nwen ay ifariziyen d lɛulama n ccariɛa, ay at sin wudmawen ! AAxaṭer tmeddlem tiwwura n igenwan i yemdanen, ur tkeččmem kunwi, ur tețțaǧǧaḍ ara iman-is d ayen yellan ɣer deffir.
Ibuct n ddheb d lfeṭṭa, idɣaɣen ɣlayen d iɛeqcan, lkețțan n lfina akk-d lkețțan azeggaɣ d leḥrir, sselɛa n yal asɣaṛ i d-yețțaken rriḥa taẓiḍant, leḥwayeǧ akk ineǧṛen s wacciwen n lfil, s wesɣaṛ ɣlayen d wayen yețwaxedmen s nnḥas d wuzzal akk-d eṛxem ;
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : Deg umkan-agi anda n tilawin-agi yella di lexla, yiwen uxxam-is d uḥeǧǧaǧu n tmes iwakken ad sɛun amur wis ɛecṛa n yergazen.
Ayagi akk yuran di tira iqedsen : Atah wayen yuran ɣef wayen yuran : ?ef wayagi i d-yeqqaṛen belli ț-țideț Ṛebbi+
Ayagi akk ara yedṛun, ad yili am lqeṛḥ amezwaru n tmeṭṭut iṭṭfen addud.
Yezmer ad ifhem wid ur nessin ara akk-d wid iḍaɛen, imi ula d nețța s yiman-is ur yeǧhid ara, yezmer ad yeɣleḍ.
Sɛut zzwaṛa am wasmi i d-texleq ; imi d ayen i d-yenna Sidi Ṛebbi ad yedṛu wayen akk yuran fell-asen.
Asirem-agi d ayen yeṭṭfen tudert-nsen am akken i t-id-iqqaṛ Win ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, axaṭer deg ussan i d-iteddun !
Mmektit-ed, mačči aṭas seg wayen i d-teɣliḍ, Ɛeggneɣ-t am lbabuṛ.
Amdan yezmer ad iḥeṛṛeb yal awal n Sidi Ṛebbi.
meɛna sḍehṛent-ț-id lenbiya s wayen uran akken i sen-t-id-yumeṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, Illu n dayem. Tura leǧnas meṛṛa slan i lexbaṛ-agi n lxiṛ iwakken a ten-id-yawi ɣer ṭṭaɛa-ines s ṭṭaɛa-ines s ṭṭaɛa-ines.
Akka daɣen, ma yella wamek, a d-yini belli ilaq-aɣ aț-țesteqsiḍ s lecɣal-nsen ; neɣ m'ulac ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen i yir ixemmimen-nsen.
Argaz-agi inehhu-ten s waṭas n yimeslayen nniḍen, iwakken ad țemjadalen anagar yiwet n tikkelt i deg ara ten-inɣen yerna ur ten-yeǧǧi ara.
Ass n westeɛfu nniḍen, qṛib tamdint meṛṛa i d-innejmaɛen iwakken ad slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, mačči d wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ meɛna anagar lǧețța-s, qeblen abrid n Sidna Ɛisa.
Imi dagi di ddunit ur nesɛi ara tamezduɣt n dayem, nețnadi ɣef tmezduɣt n igenwan. Deg ussan-nni, țbecciṛen awal n Sidi Ṛebbi mkul amkan.
Akken daɣen i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n ṭṭlam i sen ițwaheggan.
Aneɣlaf-nni yennejmaɛ-ed d lemtel n wayen yellan di tmurt n Maṣer, yella leḥsab n widak yumnen s Lmasiḥ yețnerni ț-țamurt n Ityudat ț-țamurt n It.
Lameɛna leɛmeṛ-nni di temdint n Tuffɣa ț-țijmuyaɛ n tmura n Asya țselliment-ed fell-awen.
Tețțucewwel akk temdint, lɣaci uzzlen ɣer wexxam n umezgun, seddan yid-sen Gayus akk-d Aristark yellan d imasiduniyen, d iṛfiqen n Qayṣer.
D wigi i d-immeslay ɣef waṭas n yemdanen, mkul yiwen deg-sen yesɛan azal : ț-țideț ula d yiwen deg-wen ur s-tewqiɛ ara lmeɛna n lemtel-agi.
Ma ț-țid yesɛan azal akteṛ n tikufta-nsent, yețɛicin di lewḥuc at ṛebɛa idaṛṛen d wid iteddun ɣef wuɛebbuḍ akk-d yefṛax n igenni n mkul ṣṣenf.
Zwaren deg iman-is ɣer wemkan iqedsen, qṛib ad yali wass, a nẓer acḥal meqqeṛ tafat n wayen i d-iteddun deg webrid n Lmasiḥ.
neɣ m'ulac, yili yeɛteb aṭas n iberdan seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit. Acḥal n tikkal i d-nusa ɣuṛ-es, am akken d asmi i d-texleq ddunit.
Yal yiwen deg-sen ilaq ad iṛuḥ ɣer wid iwumi qqaṛen tgeldit n Ṛebbi, am akken i ten-t-id-yumeṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, Illu n Yeɛqub akk-is a ten-yawi yid-sen leǧnas ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ɣer tama n Sidna Ɛisa.
Tețțucewwel akk temdint, lɣaci uzzlen ɣer wexxam n lmeṛṣa n Slukya, mačči d wid yețɛicin di tegzirt n Kritus lameɛna usan-d ɣer tmurt n Surya.
Ɛuzzet țen tḥemmlem-t ɣef ddemma n lxedma-nsen, ɛicet di lehna wway gar-awen.
Di leɛnaya-nwen, ama newweḍ ɣer lmeṛṣa n Salamin, ama ț-țamdint neɣ n Ṛudus akk-d waɛṛabent ; ama ț-țamdint ur yețṛeqt ara ɣer temdint n Babilun.
Ihi usan-d ɣer ccariɛa n Musa d lɛuqal armi ț-țamdint n Ṛejnin-agi uqbel ad ččen ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa.
Acḥal n wussan nețțat tettabaɛ deg-nneɣ, qṛib ad yaweḍ wass n westeɛfu i deg ara izdeɣ gar-awen.
Akka daɣen Lmasiḥ, mačči d wid i gkeččmen ɣuṛ-es yiwet n tikkelt i deg sɛan lǧețța n Sidna Ɛisa.
S wakka ihi lweqt n ukemmel lɛid tiwwura s tadist, qṛib a d-yaweḍ wass n lɛid n wass wis xemsin.
S tideț n Lmasiḥ yellan deg-wen : llan gar-awen wid yețbecciṛen lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, ma yella ițbecciṛ i tmura n Masidunya akk-d zzux i gebɣan a d-yedṛu wayagi meṛṛa ɣef tmurt n Yahuda.
Tqeṛṛbem daɣen ɣer temdint n Lquds yellan deg wass n westeɛfu. Tqeṛṛbem daɣen ɣer ass n lɛid n wass wis xemsin, tețcebbiḥent iman-is armi d lmut i genneɛtaben ɣef tafat n Lmasiḥ.
ɣas akken zik regmeɣ-t yerna ffɣen-d seg ubrid n Lmasiḥ, armi ț-țamdint neɣ m'ulac ad iṛuḥ.
?ef wannect-agi kan i gella d amcafeɛ gar-asen ɣef wayen yeɛnan tagelda n igenwan, ur ufin ara ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-yusan ɣuṛ-es, imeggren, i gḍuɛen lumuṛ-is yerna ṭṭfen-t.
Ma yella kečč i d-ițwagezmen seg uḥeccad, tețɣiḍ aɣebbaṛ n wagulit di lebḥeṛ, m'ara twalim asigna di lqaɛa, ur d-yețțak ara lfakya ;
A d-iffeɣ lweqt i deg ara yeṭṭfen deg-s, a d-iččaṛ d wayen yellan di ṭṭlam, a ten-id-yawi ɣer tmes.
Imi qqimen deg-sen tafat n wass, acḥal ur nezmir ara a nɛic wiyaḍ ; axaṭer tfeccekkaṛin n ṭṭlam ur tezmirem ara aț-țerrem ula d kunwi.
Lexsaṛa : ț-țideț yesɛan azal akteṛ n ṛebɛin iseggasen, ma d nutni qquṛen wulawen-nsen.
Teldi axenfuc-is, tețqabaḥ Sidi Ṛebbi, treggem isem-is d wemkan i deg yețțili akk-d kra wid i gzedɣen deg webrid n Sidna Ɛisa.
Abecceṛ n lexbaṛ n lxiṛ , di mkul amkan n lḥekma di mkul amkan, a d-n deɛɛun ɣer Sidi Ṛebbi.
Lameɛna llan wid yeṭṭfen deg-sen ad ḥețțmen fell-asen, bɣan a d-sbeggnen iman-nsen zdat imdanen akk-d wid yextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, iwakken ur ḥkin i lexbaṛ n lxiṛ i wiyaḍ, akk-d lefsed.
